{fc9When CP (Critical Points) charge to max during battle, 
you will enter a "Cross Art Standby" state. 
Press {r2} to pull the trigger and fire off the Cross Art.}

CP (Critical Points) increase when you perform actions in battle,
such as attack or heal.

{fc9The best way to earn CP is to strike an enemy's weak point.}

Selecting your Digimon and skills with compatibilities between 
Attributes and Elements in mind will make it easier to charge CP.

{fc9Any CP you have charged will carry over to the next battle.}

