Create new partner Digimon based on battle data.

{fc9Digimon can be Converted once their Scan Rate is between 
100% to 200% (the maximum).}

Command your partner Digimon to utilize a skill attack.

{fc9Use {r2} DigiAttack as a preemptive strike against a hostile Digimon,
or to destroy or activate objects.}

Press or hold {r1} DigiRide to ride atop a partner Digimon.

{fc9You can DigiAttack and Analyze while DigiRiding.}
{fc9You can also DigiAttack by colliding with hostile Digimon or objects.}

Each Digimon possesses an affinity with each of the elements:

